These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Movie-Genre: epic, mystery, sports, horror
Birthday: january, august, april, december
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is between Movie-Genre:epic and Birthday:august##2
2. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left or right of Birthday:january##3
3. Movie-Genre:mystery is somewhere between Movie-Genre:horror and Movie-Genre:epic##7
4. Birthday:august is in an even position##4
5. Movie-Genre:horror is on the right of Birthday:april##1
6. Birthday:august is somewhere to the left of Birthday:january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | horror       | mystery | epic        |
| Birthday      | april  | august | december        | january |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Color: amber, purple, turquise, black
Music-Genre: metal, blues, classical, electronic
1. Music-Genre:electronic is somewhere between Music-Genre:classical and Color:turquise##7
2. Color:black is somewhere to the left of Color:amber##5
3. Color:black is somewhere to the right of Music-Genre:electronic##5
4. Color:purple is on the left of Color:black##1
5. Music-Genre:electronic is between Music-Genre:classical and Music-Genre:blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Color     | turquise | purple       | black         | amber     |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | electronic | classical | metal |

