.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
City: rome, marseilles, venice, liverpool
Game: monopoly, poker, snooker, billiard
1. Game:billiard is on the far left or far right##3
2. City:rome is somewhere between Game:poker and City:liverpool##7
3. City:venice == Game:billiard##1
4. Game:snooker is on the left of Game:billiard##1
5. City:marseilles is on the left of Game:monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| City   | marseilles | rome | liverpool       | venice |
| Game   | poker      | monopoly   | snooker | billiard  |

