Color: blood-red, brown, black, pink
1. Music-Genre:metal != Color:pink##6
2. Color:black is on the left or right of Color:pink##3
3. Music-Genre:salsa == Color:black##1
4. Music-Genre:punk is somewhere between Music-Genre:salsa and Music-Genre:techno##7
5. Music-Genre:metal is on the left of Music-Genre:techno##1
6. Color:pink is on the right of Color:black##1
7. Color:pink is on the left of Color:blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | punk | metal | techno |
| Color           | black   | pink    | blood-red       | brown  |

