2. Beverage:water != House:futuristic##6
3. House:cape-cod != Beverage:tea##6
4. Beverage:tea is somewhere to the right of House:craftsman##5
5. Beverage:fanta == House:ranch-style##1
6. Beverage:mirinda is somewhere to the right of House:ranch-style##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | mirinda | water | tea |
| House           | ranch-style    | cape-cod   | craftsman  | futuristic      |

